cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use this software, please cite it using the metadata below."
title: "SOPARC Dual-Video Coding Tool"
abstract: >
  An open-source browser-based adaptation of the System for Observing Play
  and Recreation in Communities (SOPARC) protocol, extended to support
  dual-angle video coding, video synchronisation, and dwell-time measurement.
  Developed for the More Sport Their Way Research Project at Edith Cowan University.
